    <note>Tao(1) Bi [26942] Hunan TZ, 134.5a has him earning the jinshi before he was born. He was fond of reading military classics in youth. Ding(1) Wei [1641] valued him and arranged the marriage between Bi and the daughter of Wei's elder brother, D [26943]. His daughter, who was betrothed to Yan(2) Jie [25139], must have died before the marriage since Jie is not listed as a son-in-law in the funerary inscription drafted by Liu Zhi somewhat later than the one drafted by Huang Tingjian. Liu Zhi, WJ, 12.1a-6b; Huang Tingjian, WJ, 22.15b-19b. CBD, 3, 2675.</note>
